<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Luna Portal — Concept</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --bg:#f2f6fc;--bg2:#e8f0f9;--surface:#ffffff;--surface2:#f8fafd;
  --border:#e2e8f0;--border2:#cbd5e1;--text:#0f172a;--text2:#475569;--text3:#94a3b8;
  --accent:#6d28d9;--accent-light:#ede9fe;--accent-mid:#7c3aed;
  --grn:#059669;--grn-bg:#ecfdf5;--grn-border:#a7f3d0;
  --pnk:#be185d;--pnk-bg:#fdf2f8;--pnk-border:#fbcfe8;
  --amb:#b45309;--amb-bg:#fffbeb;--amb-border:#fde68a;
  --red:#dc2626;--red-bg:#fef2f2;--red-border:#fecaca;
  --blu:#1d4ed8;--blu-bg:#eff6ff;--blu-border:#bfdbfe;
}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'SF Pro Text',system-ui,sans-serif;min-height:100vh;font-size:14px}
.topnav{height:52px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 28px;background:rgba(242,246,252,0.88);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;backdrop-filter:blur(16px)}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer}
.logo-mark{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:7px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#4f46e5);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fff}
.logo-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.3px;color:var(--text)}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:2px}
.navbtn{padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;background:none;border:none;transition:all .15s;font-weight:500}
.navbtn:hover{color:var(--text);background:rgba(0,0,0,0.05)}
.navbtn.active{background:var(--text);color:#fff}
.nav-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.user-chip{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:4px 12px 4px 4px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;cursor:pointer}
.user-av{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#4f46e5);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#fff}
.tier-pill{padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.4px;background:var(--accent-light);color:var(--accent)}
.app{display:flex;min-height:calc(100vh - 52px)}
.sidebar{width:210px;flex-shrink:0;background:var(--surface);border-right:1px solid var(--border);padding:16px 10px;position:sticky;top:52px;height:calc(100vh - 52px);overflow-y:auto}
.sb-user{padding:8px 10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:10px}
.sb-email{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3)}
.sb-profile{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-top:5px;cursor:pointer}
.sb-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0}
.sb-pname{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text)}
.sb-chevron{margin-left:auto;font-size:10px;color:var(--text3)}
.sb-section{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);padding:12px 10px 5px}
.sb-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;margin-bottom:1px}
.sb-item:hover{color:var(--text);background:rgba(0,0,0,0.04)}
.sb-item.active{color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-light);font-weight:600}
.sb-count{margin-left:auto;font-size:10px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.07);color:var(--text3);padding:1px 7px;border-radius:10px}
.main{flex:1;padding:28px 32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;overflow-x:hidden;max-width:1100px}
.screen{display:none}.screen.active{display:contents}
.card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px}
.card-pad{padding:18px 20px}
.card-h{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px}
.card-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text)}
.card-action{font-size:12px;color:var(--accent);cursor:pointer;font-weight:500}
.row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.btn{padding:6px 14px;border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all .15s}
.btn-p{background:var(--text);color:#fff}.btn-p:hover{opacity:.85}
.btn-g{background:var(--surface);color:var(--text2);border:1px solid var(--border)}.btn-g:hover{background:var(--surface2)}
.btn-d{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red);border:1px solid var(--red-border)}
.btn-accent{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}.btn-accent:hover{opacity:.9}
.btn-sm{padding:4px 10px;font-size:11px;border-radius:7px}
.badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;padding:2px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.3px;white-space:nowrap}
.b-pur{background:var(--accent-light);color:var(--accent)}
.b-grn{background:var(--grn-bg);color:var(--grn);border:1px solid var(--grn-border)}
.b-pnk{background:var(--pnk-bg);color:var(--pnk);border:1px solid var(--pnk-border)}
.b-amb{background:var(--amb-bg);color:var(--amb);border:1px solid var(--amb-border)}
.b-blu{background:var(--blu-bg);color:var(--blu);border:1px solid var(--blu-border)}
.b-gray{background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text3);border:1px solid var(--border)}
.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:16px}
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:14px}
.g4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:12px}
.g6{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(6,minmax(0,1fr));gap:10px}
.stat{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center}
.stat-v{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-1px;color:var(--text)}
.stat-l{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:2px}
.av{border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0}
.toggle{width:32px;height:18px;border-radius:10px;position:relative;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0}
.t-on{background:var(--accent)}.t-off{background:var(--border2)}
.t-knob{position:absolute;top:2px;width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;transition:left .15s;box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
.t-on .t-knob{left:16px}.t-off .t-knob{left:2px}
.page-h{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between}
.page-title{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.4px;color:var(--text)}
.page-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:4px}
.label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.6px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:5px}
.input{width:100%;padding:8px 12px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;color:var(--text);font-size:13px;outline:none}
.input:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
.chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:3px 9px 3px 5px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer}
.chip:hover{border-color:var(--accent)}
.chip-av{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:9px;font-weight:600}
.tabs{display:flex;gap:2px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.05);border-radius:9px;padding:3px;width:fit-content;margin-bottom:16px}
.tab{padding:5px 14px;border-radius:7px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}
.tab.on{background:var(--surface);color:var(--text);box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
.hero{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:24px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px}
.pc{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:18px 14px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.pc:hover,.pc.sel{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--accent-light)}
.pc-av{width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto 10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:19px;font-weight:600}
.plan{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:22px 18px;transition:all .2s;cursor:pointer;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.plan:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.plan.cur{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--accent-light)}
.plan-top-bar{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#7c3aed,#4f46e5)}
.addon{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:13px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;transition:all .15s}
.addon:hover{border-color:var(--accent)}
.addon-logo{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:17px}
.coll-row{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:6px;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .15s,box-shadow .15s}
.coll-row:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.coll-row.open{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--accent-light)}
.coll-row.dragging{opacity:.35;border-style:dashed}
.coll-row.drag-over{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--accent-light)}
.coll-main{display:flex;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;user-select:none}
.coll-handle{width:36px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--text3);cursor:grab;flex-shrink:0;padding:14px 4px 14px 10px;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:-1px}
.coll-handle:active{cursor:grabbing}
.coll-thumb{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:19px;flex-shrink:0}
.coll-info{flex:1;padding:11px 10px;min-width:0}
.coll-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.coll-name-input{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--accent);border-radius:6px;padding:2px 7px;outline:none;background:var(--accent-light);width:200px}
.coll-meta{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:2px}
.coll-actions{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding-right:12px;flex-shrink:0}
.coll-chevron{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);transition:transform .2s;flex-shrink:0;margin-right:4px}
.coll-row.open .coll-chevron{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.coll-editor{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:20px 20px 20px 20px;background:var(--surface2);display:none}
.coll-row.open .coll-editor{display:block}
.src-list{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:11px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:10px}
.src-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:9px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:background .1s}
.src-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.src-item:hover{background:var(--surface2)}
.src-item.dragging{opacity:.3}
.src-item.drag-over{background:var(--accent-light)}
.src-handle{color:var(--text3);cursor:grab;font-size:13px;flex-shrink:0;letter-spacing:-1px}
.src-handle:active{cursor:grabbing}
.col-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 240px;gap:24px}
.src-chip{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);margin:3px 3px 0 0}
.upload-zone{border:1.5px dashed var(--border2);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text3);font-size:12px;transition:border-color .15s;background:var(--surface2)}
.upload-zone:hover{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-light)}
.inv-code{font-family:monospace;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-light);padding:6px 13px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(109,40,217,.2)}
.tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
.tbl th{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);padding:9px 16px;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.tbl td{padding:11px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);vertical-align:middle}
.tbl tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
.tbl tr:hover td{background:var(--surface2)}
.bill-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:13px}
.bill-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.src-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.src-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.u-row{padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.u-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.u-main{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.u-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-top:8px;padding-left:42px}
.tier-sm{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:13px;padding:16px;text-align:center}
.tier-count{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-1px;margin:6px 0 3px;color:var(--text)}

/* PURCHASE / CONSUMER FLOW */
.purchase-hero{text-align:center;padding:48px 24px 32px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px}
.ph-eyebrow{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:10px}
.ph-title{font-size:32px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.8px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.2}
.ph-sub{font-size:16px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:10px;line-height:1.6}
.toggle-billing{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.05);border-radius:20px;padding:4px;margin:20px auto 0;width:fit-content}
.tb-opt{padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text2);transition:all .15s}
.tb-opt.on{background:var(--text);color:#fff}
.save-pill{background:#dcfce7;color:#166534;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:4px}
.plan-featured-wrap{position:relative;padding-top:14px}
.plan-most-pop{position:absolute;top:0;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--text);color:#fff;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 12px;border-radius:20px;white-space:nowrap;z-index:1}
.plan-big{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;padding:28px 22px;transition:all .2s;cursor:pointer;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.plan-big:hover{box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.1);transform:translateY(-3px)}
.plan-big.featured{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--accent-light)}
.plan-big-icon{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:14px}
.plan-big-name{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text)}
.plan-big-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin:5px 0 18px;line-height:1.5}
.plan-big-price-wrap{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:1px;margin-bottom:2px}
.plan-big-dollar{font-size:36px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1.5px;color:var(--text)}
.plan-big-cents{font-size:18px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text3)}
.plan-big-per{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:20px}
.pf-big{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:9px}
.fy-big{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent-light);color:var(--accent);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.fn-big{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.cta-btn{width:100%;padding:12px;border-radius:10px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;border:none;cursor:pointer;margin-top:20px;transition:all .15s}
.cta-primary{background:var(--text);color:#fff}.cta-primary:hover{opacity:.85}
.cta-ghost{background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text2);border:1px solid var(--border)}.cta-ghost:hover{background:var(--border)}
.cta-accent{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}.cta-accent:hover{opacity:.9}
.invite-input-row{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:12px}
.invite-input{flex:1;padding:10px 14px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;font-size:14px;color:var(--text);outline:none;font-family:monospace;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}
.invite-input:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
.feature-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px}
.feat-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:16px}
.feat-icon{font-size:20px;margin-bottom:8px}
.feat-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text)}
.feat-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:3px;line-height:1.5}
.faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:14px 0}
.faq-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.faq-q{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text)}
.faq-a{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:5px;line-height:1.6}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="topnav">
  <div class="logo" onclick="goScreen('purchase')">
    <div class="logo-mark">L</div>
    <span class="logo-name">Luna</span>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <button class="navbtn active" id="nav-purchase" onclick="goScreen('purchase')">Home</button>
    <button class="navbtn" id="nav-account" onclick="goScreen('overview')">Account</button>
    <button class="navbtn" id="nav-catalogs" onclick="goScreen('catalogs')">Catalogs</button>
    <button class="navbtn" id="nav-admin" onclick="goScreen('users')">Admin</button>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <span class="tier-pill">ADMIN</span>
    <div class="user-chip">
      <div class="user-av">Z</div>
      <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text)">Zain</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="app">
<aside class="sidebar">
  <div class="sb-user">
    <div class="sb-email">zainalkafaji19@gmail.com</div>
    <div class="sb-profile">
      <div class="sb-dot"></div>
      <span class="sb-pname">Zain (main)</span>
      <span class="sb-chevron">▾</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="sb-section">Account</div>
  <div class="sb-item active" id="sb-purchase" onclick="goScreen('purchase')">🏠 Home</div>
  <div class="sb-item" id="sb-overview" onclick="goScreen('overview')">⊞ Overview</div>
  <div class="sb-item" id="sb-profiles" onclick="goScreen('profiles')">◉ My profiles</div>
  <div class="sb-item" id="sb-sub" onclick="goScreen('sub')">💳 Subscription</div>
  <div class="sb-item" id="sb-invites" onclick="goScreen('invites')">🎟 Invite codes <span class="sb-count">3</span></div>
  <div class="sb-section">Content</div>
  <div class="sb-item" id="sb-addons" onclick="goScreen('addons')">🧩 Addons <span class="sb-count">9</span></div>
  <div class="sb-item" id="sb-catalogs" onclick="goScreen('catalogs')">📁 Catalogs <span class="sb-count">24</span></div>
  <div class="sb-item">📊 Watch history</div>
  <div class="sb-item">🔖 Library</div>
  <div class="sb-section">Admin</div>
  <div class="sb-item" id="sb-users" onclick="goScreen('users')">👥 Users</div>
  <div class="sb-item">📈 Analytics</div>
  <div class="sb-item">⚙️ Settings</div>
</aside>

<main class="main">

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
     SCREEN: CONSUMER / PURCHASE FLOW
═══════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="screen active" id="sc-purchase">

  <div class="purchase-hero">
    <div class="ph-eyebrow">Luna Streaming</div>
    <h1 class="ph-title">Your content, your way.</h1>
    <p class="ph-sub">Choose a plan and start watching in minutes.<br>No ads. No lock-in. Cancel any time.</p>
    <div class="toggle-billing">
      <div class="tb-opt on" onclick="setBilling('monthly',this)">Monthly</div>
      <div class="tb-opt" onclick="setBilling('yearly',this)">Yearly <span class="save-pill">Save 20%</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1.05fr 1fr;gap:14px;align-items:start">

    <!-- PREMIUM -->
    <div class="plan-big">
      <div class="plan-top-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,#f472b6,#ec4899)"></div>
      <div class="plan-big-icon" style="background:#fdf2f8">✨</div>
      <div class="plan-big-name">Premium</div>
      <div class="plan-big-desc">Works instantly — everything pre-configured for you</div>
      <div class="plan-big-price-wrap">
        <span class="plan-big-dollar" id="price-premium-dollar">$4</span><span class="plan-big-cents" id="price-premium-cents">.99</span>
      </div>
      <div class="plan-big-per" id="per-premium">per month</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Up to 3 profiles</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Content ready on sign-in</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Curated catalogs included</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Full playback quality</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fn-big">✕</div>Custom addon management</div>
      <button class="cta-btn cta-ghost">Get started</button>
    </div>

    <!-- PREMIUM+ (featured) -->
    <div class="plan-featured-wrap">
      <div class="plan-most-pop">Most popular</div>
      <div class="plan-big featured">
        <div class="plan-top-bar"></div>
        <div class="plan-big-icon" style="background:var(--accent-light)">⚡</div>
        <div class="plan-big-name">Premium+</div>
        <div class="plan-big-desc">Full control — install and manage your own sources</div>
        <div class="plan-big-price-wrap">
          <span class="plan-big-dollar" id="price-powerplus-dollar">$9</span><span class="plan-big-cents" id="price-powerplus-cents">.99</span>
        </div>
        <div class="plan-big-per" id="per-powerplus">per month</div>
        <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Up to 5 profiles</div>
        <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Manage own addons and sources</div>
        <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>All curated catalogs</div>
        <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Full playback quality</div>
        <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Priority support</div>
        <button class="cta-btn cta-accent">Get started</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAMILY -->
    <div class="plan-big">
      <div class="plan-top-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,#34d399,#059669)"></div>
      <div class="plan-big-icon" style="background:#ecfdf5">👨‍👩‍👧</div>
      <div class="plan-big-name">Family</div>
      <div class="plan-big-desc">Share Luna with up to 7 people — they inherit your setup</div>
      <div class="plan-big-price-wrap">
        <span class="plan-big-dollar" id="price-family-dollar">$14</span><span class="plan-big-cents" id="price-family-cents">.99</span>
      </div>
      <div class="plan-big-per" id="per-family">per month</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Unlimited profiles</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Invite up to 7 family members</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Members use your addons</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>All Premium+ features</div>
      <div class="pf-big"><div class="fy-big">✓</div>Per-profile PIN lock</div>
      <button class="cta-btn cta-primary">Get started</button>
    </div>

    <!-- INVITE CODE -->
    <div class="plan-big" style="background:var(--surface2);border-style:dashed">
      <div class="plan-big-icon" style="background:var(--accent-light);font-size:18px">🎟</div>
      <div class="plan-big-name">Have an invite?</div>
      <div class="plan-big-desc">A friend shared Luna with you — enter your code to get access</div>
      <div style="margin-top:8px">
        <div class="label">Invite code</div>
        <div class="invite-input-row">
          <input class="invite-input" placeholder="LUNA-XXXX">
          <button class="btn btn-p" style="white-space:nowrap">Redeem</button>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:8px">Your friend's plan access will be applied to your account.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <div>
    <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:14px;color:var(--text)">What's included in every plan</div>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">📱</div><div class="feat-title">All your devices</div><div class="feat-desc">iPhone, iPad, Mac, Apple TV — one subscription, everywhere.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">📁</div><div class="feat-title">Curated catalogs</div><div class="feat-desc">Hand-picked collections built by the Luna team, updated regularly.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">🔤</div><div class="feat-title">Subtitles and sync</div><div class="feat-desc">Subtitle support across all content, synced to your profile.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">🔖</div><div class="feat-title">Watchlist and progress</div><div class="feat-desc">Save shows, track what you've watched, pick up right where you left off.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">👤</div><div class="feat-title">Multiple profiles</div><div class="feat-desc">Each person gets their own watchlist, addons, and avatar.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">🔒</div><div class="feat-title">PIN-protected profiles</div><div class="feat-desc">Lock any profile with a PIN to keep your watch history private.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div class="card card-pad">
    <div class="card-h"><span class="card-title">Common questions</span></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What's the difference between Premium and Premium+?</div><div class="faq-a">Premium is pre-configured — content is ready the moment you sign in, no setup needed. Premium+ gives you full control to install and manage your own addons and content sources.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How do invite codes work?</div><div class="faq-a">If a Family plan subscriber invites you, you'll receive a code granting Friends and Family access — which means you get access to their configured content without paying separately.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Can I switch plans later?</div><div class="faq-a">Yes. You can upgrade or downgrade any time from the Subscription page. Changes take effect at the start of your next billing cycle.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item" style="border:none"><div class="faq-q">Is there a free trial?</div><div class="faq-a">New accounts get a 7-day free trial on any paid plan. No credit card required to start.</div></div>
  </div>

</section>

